---
title: Homemade Pork Rissoles & Roast Veggie Toss with Almonds & Herby Mayo
description: Dinner doesn’t have to a boring chore anymore. Roll up your sleeves and enjoy crafting your own pork rissoles. You can do this
while the veggies roast in the oven. Finish off your masterpiece with a drizzle of herby mayo.
